CHANGES
=======

* Only refresh the widgets of the inbox that change
* Wrap subject when the line's too long
* Remove premature optimisation with email flags
* Start introducing type annotations
* Set the types in docstrings the right way around
* Bring MaildirEmail up to parity with ImapEmail
* Mark an email as read once opened
* Show the "To" header in the detail window
* Add CLI args to specify where to get emails from
* Add a basic window for displaying the email body

